WorkItem.Description:
We have received an example of an Excel file where reading using PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5 fails a whole with the following error:
 
Fatal error: Call to a member function getData() on a non-object in /var/www/phpexcel/Classes/PHPExcel/Reader/Excel5.php on line 723
 
In the particular example, the reason was that there was an EMF (Enhanced Metafile) image in the workbook.
 
Environment:
----
PHPExcel 1.6.6
WorkItem.Summary: PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5 fails as a whole when workbook contains images other than JPEG/PNG
